# Password Generator

***

This class was made to generate alphanumeric sequences for use as password.

As you'll see in the example, you can use them to generate passwords based in the letters of your name, phrases, date of your birth in a safe way.

Visit my site: [http://www.wildiney.com](http://www.wildiney.com)
